6.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157772376/image_157772376.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157772376/image_157772376.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157772376/image_157772376.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alina555</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I last wrote about VICI Properties Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VICI\" title=\"VICI Properties Inc.\">VICI</a></span>) in January in my article \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4661462-vici-properties-reviewing-my-position\">VICI Properties: Reviewing My Position</a>\". Back then, I took a rather cautious stance regarding VICI, which was expressed by my \"hold\" rating.</p> <p>VICI is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157772376/image_157772376.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743186-vici-why-i-am-selling-this-dividend-darling", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 10:52:51"}, {"id": "4743185", "title": "Costamare: Attractive Valuations And A 3.5% Dividend Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/660791312/image_660791312.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Black cargo ship\" data-id=\"660791312\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/660791312/image_660791312.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/6